.DT
reform_message
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
reform_message

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
reform_message -  This method does all those terrible things with messages and $'s turning them into real strings.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
mixed reform_message(string message,
mixed things)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^message%^RESET%^ - the message to reform
%^BOLD%^things%^RESET%^ - some bonus things to reform it with
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
an array consisting of two elements

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/global/player/events.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method does all those terrible things with messages and $'s
turning them into real strings.  It is a neat function if somewhat
complicated :)  It was written by Deutha.


The return array has two elements, the first being the reformed message and the second being the reformed things array.
.EP

